TextEng: I have recovered one of the reagents for the cure.
<StartAction>Explain about the Cockatrice in the Docks district.</Start>
<StartAction>Explain about the Dryad in the Blacklake district.</Start>
<StartAction>Explain about the Intellect Devourer in the prison.</Start>
<StartAction>Explain about the Yuan-Ti in the Beggar's Nest.</Start>
I need to talk to you.
I came as quickly as I could, Lady Aribeth.
Me got one of them Waterdeep monster things for cure!
Text: 나 치료제 위한 워터딥 괴물 하나 잡았어!

TextEng: Me need talk at you.
I have the last of the reagents from the Waterdhavian creatures.
Text: 워터딥의 생명체들에서 나온 마지막 재료를 가져왔습니다.

TextEng: Me gots last Waterdeep monster thing!
<StartAction>Explain about the Yuan-Ti in the Beggar's Nest.</Start>
<StartAction>Explain about the Intellect Devourer in the prison.</Start>
<StartAction>Explain about the Dryad in the Blacklake district.</Start>
<StartAction>Explain about the Cockatrice in the Docks district.</Start>
I was delayed by Fenthick.
You were waiting for me? Why?
I'm here now. Say what you have to say.
Me come as quick as me can.
Fenthick want talk at me first.
Why you wait for me?
Me here now. You speak.
It will be an honor to serve you, Lady Aribeth!
I serve no master but myself!
Text: 나는 나 자신 외엔 누구의 명도 받지 않아!

TextEng: I'll help you... for a price.
Me be honored for serve you, Aribeth!
Me serve no one but me!
Text: 나, 나 말곤 아무도 안 섬겨!

TextEng: Me help you... if you give gold!
I have heard such rumors before.
What became of these creatures?
Time's wasting. Get to the point, Aribeth.
Text: 시간이 없습니다. 본론으로 들어가시죠, 아리베스 경.

TextEng: Me heard that before.
What happen to magic monsters?
You boring. Hurry up.
And then the Academy was attacked.
So you think someone within the Academy betrayed you.
Text: 그러니까 사관학교 내부에 배신자가 있다고 보시는군요.

TextEng: But Academy got attacked.
Me not understand - you say Academy betray you?
Text: 이해 안 돼-사관학교가 널 배신했다는 거야?

TextEng: How may I serve you in this, Lady Aribeth?
Text: 제가 어떻게 도와드리면 되겠습니까, 아리베스 경?

TextEng: Let me guess, you want me to get those creatures back.
Text: 짐작컨대, 그 생명체들을 되찾아 오길 바라시는군요.

TextEng: What you want me do now, Aribeth?
You want me go get monster back for you?
Why did you choose me for this?
Shouldn't the city watch be helping in this?
Text: 이건 도시 경비대가 도와야 하는 일 아닌가요?

TextEng: I will do as you command, Lady Aribeth.
I'll do it, but the rewards better be worthwhile!
Text: 하긴 하겠지만, 보상은 그만한 가치가 있어야 합니다!

TextEng: Why you pick me?
Why city guards no do this?
Text: 왜 도시 경비대가 이거 안 해?

TextEng: Me do as you command, Aribeth.
Me do it, but it better be worth me time!
Text: 나 할게, 근데 내 시간 값은 해야 해!

TextEng: How do we even know the creatures are still alive?
Text: 그 생명체들이 아직 살아 있다는 걸 어떻게 확신하죠?

TextEng: How you even know monsters still alive?
Text: 그 괴물들이 아직 살아 있는지 넌 어떻게 알아?

TextEng: I will begin my search for the Waterdhavian creatures at once!
I need to ask you some questions.
Text: 몇 가지 여쭙고 싶은 게 있습니다.

TextEng: Me go find monsters right now!
Text: 나 지금 당장 괴물들 찾으러 간다!

TextEng: Me got questions me want ask you.
What do you think of Desther?
Tell me about Fenthick.
It would be nice to know a little more about the Lady I'm working for.
Text: 제가 모시는 분에 대해 좀 더 알면 좋을 것 같은데요.

TextEng: Now that me is working for you, me want know more 'bout you.
Text: 이제 나 너 위해 일해. 너에 대해 더 알고 싶어.

TextEng: You tell me 'bout Fenthick now, 'kay?
What you think 'bout Desther.
What can you tell me about the attack on the Academy?
Text: 사관학교가 습격당한 일에 대해 무엇을 알려 주실 수 있습니까?

TextEng: I want to know more about the Wailing Death.
Text: 울부짖는 죽음 역병에 대해 더 알고 싶습니다.

TextEng: I want more information on the Waterdhavian creatures and this cure.
Text: 워터딥의 생명체들과 이 치료법에 대해 더 자세한 정보를 듣고 싶습니다.

TextEng: Where can I get some supplies?
What you know 'bout attack on Academy?
Me want know more of plague.
What you know 'bout monsters and cure for sickness?
Text: 그 괴물들이랑 병 치료법에 대해 뭐 알아?

TextEng: Me need buy stuff.
Goodbye.
Maybe he has a point.
Maybe him got point.
Why do you put up with him?
Why you keep him here?
I want to ask you about something else.
Me want ask 'bout other stuff.
Text: 나 다른 거 물을 거 있어.

TextEng: Do have any information as to where the creatures might be?
Text: 워터딥의 생명체들이 어디에 있을지에 대한 정보가 있습니까?

TextEng: You got hints for me 'bout where to look for monsters?
Text: 그 생명체들 어디서 찾을지 힌트 있어?

TextEng: The room next door is full of plague victims. Aren't you scared of being infected?
Text: 옆방은 울부짖는 죽음 역병 환자들로 가득합니다. 감염될까 두렵지 않으십니까?

TextEng: Did the quarantine do anything to help?
You got sickies in temple here. You not scared?
Text: 여기 신전에 역병 환자들 잔뜩 있어. 너 안 무서워?

TextEng: You block city off, right? No one go in or out?
Text: 도시 봉쇄했지? 아무도 못 들어오고 못 나가지?

TextEng: Tell me about the cockatrice.
Tell me about the yuan-ti.
Tell me about the intellect devourer.
Tell me about the dryad.
What right do you have to use kill these creatures to save yourselves?
Text: 무슨 권리로 그 생명체들을 죽여서 당신들만 살겠다는 겁니까?

TextEng: You tell 'bout cockatrice.
You tell 'bout yuan-ti.
You tell 'bout intellect devourer.
You tell 'bout dryad.
You gonna kill monsters for make cure?
Text: 치료 만들려고 그 생명체들 죽일 거야?

TextEng: That's all I need to know about the Waterdhavian creatures.
Text: 워터딥의 생명체들에 관해 알아야 할 건 다 들었습니다.

TextEng: Me not need nothing else 'bout Waterdeep monsters.
Text: 워터딥의 생명체들 얘기, 더 필요 없어.

TextEng: I found a note you might be interested in.
Me got note you need look at.
Text: 나 너 봐야 할 쪽지 있어.

TextEng: Yes - let's go at once!
No - I need to take care of a couple things.
Text: 아니요 - 처리할 일이 몇 가지 있습니다.

TextEng: Yes - me ready right now!
No - me need do some stuff first.
Text: 아니 - 먼저 할 일 좀 있어.

TextEng: Thank you, Aribeth. You are most generous.
I have no need of gold. Your thanks is reward enough.
Text: 금화는 필요 없습니다. 당신의 감사면 충분한 보상입니다.

TextEng: 500 gold pieces? This is an outrage!
Me thanks you. This be lots gold.
Me not need gold. You keep for help other people.
Text: 나 금화 필요 없어. 그걸로 다른 사람 도와.

TextEng: 500 gold! This not fair! Me want more!
Text: 금화 500개! 이거 공평하지 않아! 나 더 원해!

TextEng: I require temple services.
Me need to buy temple stuff.
How it work?
How does it work?
That's handy.
Me gots hurts that need to be healed.
I am injured. Can you heal my wounds?
Text: 부상을 입었습니다. 상처를 치유해주실 수 있나요?

TextEng: Me am hurts. Yous got healing, please?
Text: 나 아파. 너 치유할 수 있어, 부탁해?

TextEng: I am injured. Could you heal me?
